'''2020年环法自行车赛'''是第107届[[环法自行车赛|环法自行车赛]]。此次比赛原定于2020年6月27日开赛，然而受[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]影响，该比赛延期至2020年8月29日开赛<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/cycling/52275648 |title=Tour de France to go ahead at end of August after coronavirus delay |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2020-04-15 |accessdate=2020-04-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729103148/https://www.bbc.com/sport/cycling/52275648 |archivedate=2020-07-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。比赛的起点位于[[尼斯|尼斯]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/cycling/50058599 |title=Tour de France: Britain's Chris Froome says 2020 Tour route is 'brutal' as he aims for fifth title |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2019-10-15 |accessdate=2019-10-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191111093756/https://www.bbc.com/sport/cycling/50058599 |archivedate=2019-11-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，终点位于[[巴黎|巴黎]][[香榭丽舍大街|香榭丽舍大街]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://edition.cnn.com/2020/08/28/sport/tour-de-france-coronavirus-protocols-spt-intl/index.html|title=Tour de France: Grappling with staging the world's toughest bike race in a pandemic|publisher=CNN|date=2020-08-28|accessdate=2020-09-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903092704/https://edition.cnn.com/2020/08/28/sport/tour-de-france-coronavirus-protocols-spt-intl/index.html|archivedate=2020-09-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>，比赛全程都在法国境内进行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.letour.fr/en/overall-route|title=Official Route of Tour de France 2020|work=Tour de France|accessdate=2020-09-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200911132820/https://www.letour.fr/en/overall-route|archivedate=2020-09-11|deadurl=unfit}}{{cbignore}}</ref>。

尽管2020年8月底时，[[2019冠状病毒病法国疫情|法国疫情]]出现反弹，该届环法仍旧按计划开赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.voanews.com/europe/covid-19-cases-rise-tour-de-france-sets|title=As COVID-19 Cases Rise, Tour de France Sets Off|publisher=[[美国之音|VOA]]|date=2020-08-29|accessdate=2020-09-20|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200920113654/https://www.voanews.com/europe/covid-19-cases-rise-tour-de-france-sets|archivedate=2020-09-20}}</ref>。为防止感染扩大，赛事主办单位出台了相应的防疫措施。参赛运动员和车队工作人员必须定期接受[[2019冠状病毒病检测|病毒检测]]，如果同一车队一周内有至少两名选手或工作人员病毒检测结果呈阳性，则该队全体成员必须接受隔离，同时该队全体成员也必须放弃后面阶段的比赛。选手在非比赛及训练场合必须戴上口罩<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/28/sports/cycling/virus-tour-de-france.html|title=Masks in Place, the Tour de France Puts On a Brave Face|publisher=The New York Times|date=2020-08-28|accessdate=2020-09-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217033923/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/28/sports/cycling/virus-tour-de-france.html|archivedate=2020-12-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。现场观赛的观众也必须时刻戴上口罩，同时媒体和观众也不允许与选手近距离互动。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.velonews.com/news/tour-de-france-outlines-how-it-will-organize-race-in-covid-era/|title=Tour de France outlines how it will organize race in COVID era|work=VeloNews|date=2020-07-14|accessdate=2020-09-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114042755/https://www.velonews.com/news/tour-de-france-outlines-how-it-will-organize-race-in-covid-era/|archivedate=2021-01-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://time.com/5884825/tour-de-france-pandemic/|title=Tour de France Begins With Strict Anti-COVID-19 Measures|publisher=Time|date=2020-08-29|accessdate=2020-09-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028000922/https://time.com/5884825/tour-de-france-pandemic/|archivedate=2020-10-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>

总共有来自22支队伍的176名自行车手参加此次比赛。最终来自[[阿聯酋航空車隊|阿聯酋航空車隊]]的斯洛文尼亚人[[塔德伊·波加薩爾|塔德伊·波加薩爾]]获得该届比赛的总冠军。波加萨尔的同胞，为{{Translink|en|Team Jumbo–Visma|Jumbo–Visma车队}}效力的[[普里莫日·羅格里奇|普里莫日·羅格里奇]]获得第二名。来自[[崔克车队|崔克车队]]的澳大利亚选手[[Richie_Porte|Richie Porte]]则获得第三名。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.uci.org/road/news/2020/tadej-pogacar-blows-the-2020-tour-de-france-apart-becoming-the-second-youngest-winner|title=Tadej Pogačar blows the 2020 Tour de France apart, becoming the second youngest winner|work=[[国际自行车联合会|UCI]]|date=2020-09-20|accessdate=2020-09-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030165908/https://www.uci.org/road/news/2020/tadej-pogacar-blows-the-2020-tour-de-france-apart-becoming-the-second-youngest-winner|archivedate=2020-10-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>

